window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Stan Weir is mourning a tragic loss when he meets a mysterious nine-year-old girl, who claims to be the reincarnated spirit of his late wife. Marcy Keef is a single mother trying to make ends meet when her daughter Erin starts describing 'past life memories'. Neither wants to believe Erin, but as violent secrets are revealed, the truth becomes harder to deny. </p> <p>With echoes of Stephen King, <i>Second Skin</i> is a propulsive thriller about grief, guilt and truths better left unknown.</p>"; 
